<P>
Motion Picture Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA033090-0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 196923 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 30, 1990, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
