SERVICE; ILLEGAL ALIENS -- UNITED STATES; AMNESTY; EMPLOYMENT DISCRIMINATION; 
RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; UNITED STATES -- LAWS; EMPLOYMENT -- ELIGIBILITY 
</P>
