<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $36 Thursday when Inquisitorial, the 
middle horse in his $6 triple, finished out of the money in the seventh race. 
Bob, who started the meeting with a mythical $1,000 bankroll, is now at 
$1,032.40. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is $60 to win on Bruho in the eighth. 
</P>
<P>
Thursday's Bankroll $1,068.40 
</P>
<P>
