<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
L.A. Gear Inc.: The Los Angeles marketer of athletic shoes and apparel said 
first-quarter net income soared 159% to $13.9 million. Revenue jumped 183% to 
$187.3 million. The firm attributed the gains to the strong increase in 
incoming orders and the reception to new product lines introduced during the 
quarter. 
</P>
