Rape of Girl -- A story in the Friday edition of The Times incorrectly reported 
that a rape victim and her accused attacker live in the same UC Irvine 
apartment complex. The apartment complex in Irvine is not affiliated with the 
university. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
